## Conversation
PR 2/4 of the Google ADK stack: exclude ADK-internal GoogleGenAI clients
from the @google/genai wrapper. See PR 1/4 (googleAdk.ts) note for the full
session context.

## Actions
Confirmed in @google/adk dist that models/google_llm.js constructs
new GoogleGenAI({..., httpOptions: this.getHttpOptions()}) where
getHttpOptions merges BaseLlm.trackingHeaders = {'x-goog-api-client':
'google-adk/<ver> gl-typescript/<node>', 'user-agent': ...}. Added
isAdkInternalClientOptions(args[0]) to the GoogleGenAI constructor proxy in
googleGenAI.ts; matching clients are returned unwrapped.

